{
  "lesson": "WC-01-06",
  "audioMaster": "training/module01-foundations/WC-01-06-full-narration-v1.0.mp3",
  "audioDurationS": 276.689,
  "method": "silencedetect -32dB/0.28s within known block windows; proportional fallback",
  "phrases": [
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p01",
      "text": "This is the Command Center, the first screen your network hands you.",
      "startS": 0,
      "endS": 3.397,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p02",
      "text": "It looks like a wall of numbers. It isn't.",
      "startS": 3.761,
      "endS": 5.458,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p03",
      "text": "It's a triage board, stacked top to bottom.",
      "startS": 5.722,
      "endS": 8.946,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p04",
      "text": "Read the stack in order, and the thing that needs you rises to the top.",
      "startS": 9.414,
      "endS": 12.726,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p05",
      "text": "First panel, the mobile app.",
      "startS": 13.276,
      "endS": 15.042,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p06",
      "text": "That Live tag means the figures move on their own, refreshing as members open the app.",
      "startS": 15.769,
      "endS": 20.308,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p07",
      "text": "You're reading its pulse right now, not a report someone ran this morning.",
      "startS": 20.805,
      "endS": 24.57,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p08",
      "text": "For a network pushing an app, this is the first read on whether members actually use it.",
      "startS": 25.195,
      "endS": 29.627,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p09",
      "text": "Four cards across.",
      "startS": 30.07,
      "endS": 31.296,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p10",
      "text": "Installs, weekly actives, redemptions, opt-in rate.",
      "startS": 32.218,
      "endS": 35.034,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p11",
      "text": "Linger on redemptions: it splits Q-R scans from kiosk taps,",
      "startS": 35.242,
      "endS": 35.989,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p12",
      "text": "so you see whether members cash in at the phone or at the machine.",
      "startS": 36.921,
      "endS": 38.276,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p13",
      "text": "That split tells you which channel is carrying the program.",
      "startS": 38.492,
      "endS": 48,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p14",
      "text": "Scroll to the map panel.",
      "startS": 48.384,
      "endS": 49.772,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p15",
      "text": "The heading counts the whole network: a hundred forty-four sites across seven states.",
      "startS": 50.665,
      "endS": 52.405,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p16",
      "text": "That color key beside it, healthy, warning, critical, is the same key the pins use.",
      "startS": 52.885,
      "endS": 55.526,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p17",
      "text": "Once you know the key, the map tells you where to look without reading a single label.",
      "startS": 56.066,
      "endS": 66.56,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p18",
      "text": "Down the left, four vitals.",
      "startS": 66.958,
      "endS": 68.804,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p19",
      "text": "Money in today, who's active, cars through the tunnels,",
      "startS": 69.115,
      "endS": 70.959,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p20",
      "text": "and the share of card charges that bounced.",
      "startS": 71.344,
      "endS": 74.569,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p21",
      "text": "That last one, the decline rate, is what a support tech watches closest,",
      "startS": 74.93,
      "endS": 79.057,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p22",
      "text": "because a climbing decline rate usually means a billing problem, not a slow day.",
      "startS": 79.368,
      "endS": 83.658,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p23",
      "text": "Now the map itself.",
      "startS": 84.096,
      "endS": 85.408,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p24",
      "text": "Every pin is a wash, colored by health, so a red dot is a site in trouble at a glance.",
      "startS": 86.517,
      "endS": 88.746,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p25",
      "text": "Hover one and it shows that site's revenue, members, and tickets, with a link to open it.",
      "startS": 89.188,
      "endS": 92.108,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p26",
      "text": "Not today, though. We're reading the network, not diving into a single site.",
      "startS": 92.683,
      "endS": 101.951,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p27",
      "text": "Click Active States, then Full USA.",
      "startS": 102.41,
      "endS": 104.531,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p28",
      "text": "The map reframes, and that's all it does.",
      "startS": 104.531,
      "endS": 107.889,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p29",
      "text": "This toggle is view-only.",
      "startS": 107.889,
      "endS": 109.559,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p30",
      "text": "It changes the shot, never the data, and never the panels below.",
      "startS": 109.559,
      "endS": 113.801,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p31",
      "text": "One click puts it back.",
      "startS": 113.801,
      "endS": 115.861,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p32",
      "text": "Here's the heart of the page.",
      "startS": 116.415,
      "endS": 117.786,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p33",
      "text": "Priority Intelligence, eleven items, four urgent.",
      "startS": 118.293,
      "endS": 119.802,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p34",
      "text": "It's your triage feed, sorted by severity,",
      "startS": 120.005,
      "endS": 122.036,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p35",
      "text": "and every row is a door onto the module where you'd actually fix it.",
      "startS": 122.671,
      "endS": 125.232,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p36",
      "text": "For a support tech, this is the panel you scan first.",
      "startS": 125.455,
      "endS": 132.604,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p37",
      "text": "Top of the feed, Critical.",
      "startS": 133.055,
      "endS": 134.566,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p38",
      "text": "Two rows, and this is where a downed P-O-S shows up first, before the phone even rings.",
      "startS": 135.017,
      "endS": 140.204,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p39",
      "text": "Open jumps you to reconciliation to work the outage.",
      "startS": 140.649,
      "endS": 143.621,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p40",
      "text": "Review drops you into Support for the tickets about to breach their S-L-A.",
      "startS": 144.058,
      "endS": 147.742,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p41",
      "text": "Next tier, High Priority.",
      "startS": 148.181,
      "endS": 150.037,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p42",
      "text": "A kiosk printer down, a site's conversion slipping.",
      "startS": 150.419,
      "endS": 156.768,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p43",
      "text": "Not on fire yet, but they will be if they sit.",
      "startS": 157.208,
      "endS": 158.523,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p44",
      "text": "Watch the verbs shift: Assign hands the work off, Analyze opens the numbers behind it.",
      "startS": 158.82,
      "endS": 162.747,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p45",
      "text": "Now the money.",
      "startS": 163.229,
      "endS": 164.139,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p46",
      "text": "Revenue Plays, five suggestions worth thirty-two hundred dollars today,",
      "startS": 164.74,
      "endS": 165.719,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p47",
      "text": "each tagged with what it's worth.",
      "startS": 166.054,
      "endS": 169.019,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p48",
      "text": "Read them as prompts, not orders.",
      "startS": 169.418,
      "endS": 170.877,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p49",
      "text": "Launch, Target, Recover, those fire real outreach to real customers,",
      "startS": 171.413,
      "endS": 173.424,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p50",
      "text": "so on a live tenant you look, you don't press.",
      "startS": 174.153,
      "endS": 182.312,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p51",
      "text": "Last group, Automations.",
      "startS": 182.744,
      "endS": 183.491,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p52",
      "text": "Two jobs already running with no one steering,",
      "startS": 183.772,
      "endS": 184.592,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p53",
      "text": "a win-back text sequence and the payment retry engine, quietly clawing back failed charges.",
      "startS": 185.21,
      "endS": 193.09,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p54",
      "text": "Inspect and View check on them without touching a thing,",
      "startS": 193.796,
      "endS": 196.413,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p55",
      "text": "which is just what you want with something already working.",
      "startS": 196.818,
      "endS": 199.352,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p56",
      "text": "One habit ties this panel together.",
      "startS": 199.778,
      "endS": 201.935,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p57",
      "text": "Read the arrow before you click.",
      "startS": 202.302,
      "endS": 204.381,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p58",
      "text": "Open, Review, View, those take you somewhere to look.",
      "startS": 204.812,
      "endS": 208.557,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p59",
      "text": "Launch, Target, Recover, Assign, those start something.",
      "startS": 208.958,
      "endS": 211.585,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p60",
      "text": "Read arrows are safe.",
      "startS": 211.874,
      "endS": 213.19,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p61",
      "text": "Action arrows you leave alone here, on a shared live tenant.",
      "startS": 213.636,
      "endS": 219.003,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s14",
      "id": "p62",
      "text": "To the right, Action Ownership.",
      "startS": 219.476,
      "endS": 220.201,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s14",
      "id": "p63",
      "text": "Same items, now answered by who owns them and when they're due.",
      "startS": 220.423,
      "endS": 221.483,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s14",
      "id": "p64",
      "text": "Regional Ops on the outage within the half hour, Support on the aging tickets,",
      "startS": 221.781,
      "endS": 225.321,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s14",
      "id": "p65",
      "text": "Marketing and Revenue on the plays.",
      "startS": 225.746,
      "endS": 235.227,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s14",
      "id": "p66",
      "text": "It answers the question a manager always asks: whose job is this.",
      "startS": 235.429,
      "endS": 236.64,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s15",
      "id": "p67",
      "text": "At the bottom, Ask MAIA.",
      "startS": 237.084,
      "endS": 239,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s15",
      "id": "p68",
      "text": "Five plain-language shortcuts, each jumping straight to the module that answers it.",
      "startS": 239.506,
      "endS": 243.885,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s15",
      "id": "p69",
      "text": "Worth flagging: the header button reads Ask Shyne, this panel reads Ask MAIA.",
      "startS": 244.571,
      "endS": 250.086,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s15",
      "id": "p70",
      "text": "Two names, so we don't tell a client they're one feature yet, and we send neither one today.",
      "startS": 250.447,
      "endS": 255.677,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s16",
      "id": "p71",
      "text": "Scroll back up, and you've got the whole board.",
      "startS": 256.129,
      "endS": 258.63,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s16",
      "id": "p72",
      "text": "App engagement, the network map, the priority feed, who owns what, and a shortcut to ask.",
      "startS": 259.166,
      "endS": 265.12,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s16",
      "id": "p73",
      "text": "Five panels, one screen.",
      "startS": 265.649,
      "endS": 267.386,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s16",
      "id": "p74",
      "text": "Read it top to bottom, and never click an arrow until you know which kind it is.",
      "startS": 267.783,
      "endS": 271.975,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s16",
      "id": "p75",
      "text": "Do that, and the Command Center works for you, not against you.",
      "startS": 272.427,
      "endS": 276.237,
      "timing": "silence"
    }
  ]
}